1961;;The Third Alibi;;British;;Montgomery Tully;;Laurence Payne, Patricia Dainton;;thriller;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/The_Third_Alibi;;Composer Norman Martell's (Laurence Payne) extra marital affair with his wife's (Patricia Dainton) sister (Jane Griffiths), results in her pregnancy. When his wife refuses to grant a divorce, Martell intricately plots her murder, using a tape recorder as his central alibi.